"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"My friend Gary Ginsbergâ€™s book, [First Friends](https://www.amazon.com/First-Friends-Powerful-Unelected-Presidents/dp/1538702924/), is out today.\\n\\nGary gave me an advance copy a few weeks ago and I have been reading it.\\n\\nFirst Friends is a book about US Presidents and their best friends who influenced them in the office.\\n\\nThe book starts with Thomas Jefferson and James Madison and ends with Bill Clinton and Vernon Jordan. In between, there are chapters about Abraham Lincoln, Woodrow Wilson, and six other Presidents and their best friends.\\n\\nMy favorite chapter was Richard Nixon and Bebe Rebozo. That is a particularly interesting story and friendship.\\n\\nIf you enjoy history books and/or are a student of the US Presidency, you should grab this book and give it a read.\\n\\nYou can do that [here](https://www.amazon.com/First-Friends-Powerful-Unelected-Presidents/dp/1538702924/).\\n\",\"timestamp\":1625655254,\"title\":\"First Friends\",\"publication\":\"avc\"},\"digest\":\"E9cH__RsILdN7Vf16mgr4ejr_Ce01XM_HcSsi8hZ5Ww\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB8332710AB60A1B2e8FE6D775d83524C9E0cE136\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FiD2ALymcePeEtTW-G9rQSmcPd1h4mDPeNiqNj5OjGw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"or7Oz7LuQf0j9f0zl2APv4Ys6kh8mj7L66G41AeIimw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"8NFDTpRvI7dQcru1LvmBUyQE7v-XsrwkiLs5Gc_0hG-z3Fw_e1HiF99HdI_KPX7orJ9qT5V3oQc-SthfNLkriw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x96db97d26aedf1dd5f41663f7ffb57a210fee4523d6bc3ef803806b7d868f6a83df05cbb0d00049a940e4fbde20b52aa0577568fd8c268b20a7371e071d217811c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on avc.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FiD2ALymcePeEtTW-G9rQSmcPd1h4mDPeNiqNj5OjGw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"or7Oz7LuQf0j9f0zl2APv4Ys6kh8mj7L66G41AeIimw\\\"}\"